<p>Hi,</p>

<p>
  Your TheraSaurus credential expires in 7 days.
  The expiration date we have on file is
  <strong><%= l @expiration_date, format: :long %></strong>.
</p>

<p>
  Please upload your renewed credential when you have it. Your credential
  status stays verified during the two week grace period. If we do not
  have an updated verified credential by
  <strong><%= l @grace_expires_date, format: :long %></strong>,
  your credential status will become expired.
</p>

<p>
  <%= link_to "Update your credential", primary_credential_url %>
</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>The TheraSaurus team</p>
